<item>
            <title>[MCOMPILER-136] The description of the skip parameter of the testCompile mojo is incorrect</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MCOMPILER-136</link>
                <project id="12317225" key="MCOMPILER">Maven Compiler Plugin (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The description of the skip parameter of TestCompilerMojo should read:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&quot;Set this to &apos;true&apos; to bypass compilation of test sources.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I also think that the text &quot;Its use is NOT RECOMMENDED, but quite convenient on occasion.&quot; should be removed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
